25%，增长了5个百分点。其中，男生从2018届的19%上升到2022届的24%；女生从2018届的22%上升到2022届的27%。 回县城安居乐业的背后，是县城工作收入水平的提高。据麦可思研究院统计数据，在县城工作的大学毕业生，月收入已从2018届的4640元上升到2022届的5377元。而就业满意度也从2018届的67%上升到2022届的76%。 那么，回县城就业的青年更偏爱哪类工作？麦可思研究院统计发现，2022届本科生在县城就业比例最高的两大行业类，分别是教育和政府公共管理。其中，“教育类”就业占比为23.6%，“政府及公共管理”就业占比为14.9%，相较于全国2022届本科毕业生在这两大行业类的就业占比，分别高出10.6和8.1个百分点。 男女在就业选择上的侧重点也有所不同。对比发现，在县城就业的女生，主要供职于教育行业，占比达到35.2%。而在县城就业的男生中，入行“政府及公共管理”的比例最高，占比达到15.3%，男性进入教育行业的占比仅有9.6%。本科生县城就业比例明显上升"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2uP5tcTJ54VWEAMaCTEwNzQzNTkzNSCu8vywBjAAOEJACXIJNjUzMjExOTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8586020ad33cd984af716a79daff9477_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1713341946.598426","card_id":"Q_653219617","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":653219617,"title":"23-24 赛季 NBA勇士 94:118 国王，如何评价这场比赛，勇士下赛季应该调整吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653219617","type":"question","created":1713328765,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":23,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,35496,130074],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I2uP5tcTJ54VWEAMaCTEwNzQzNzY0MSD9pP2wBjAAOBdACnIJNjUzMjE5NjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"85 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b17a1860009c460b033306fc10025eb6_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1713341946.598713","card_id":"Q_653210492","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f0